citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Official during the inspection process at 11:00 am on 12 May
2021. The inspector honked the vehicle horn several times and called the licensee. The licensee stated they are out of
town and will be gone for several days.
End Section
